Don't miss the latest paperback from the Queen of Suspense!
 
Henry Parker Britland IV is a dashing, debonair ex-President of the United
States. His wife Sunday is stunningly beautiful and whip-smart and she's
just been elected to Congress. And in between governing and graceful living,
the two find the time to solve some of high society's most puzzling crimes.
 
Now available in paperback, MY GAL SUNDAY boasts four sparkling stories
chronicling the capers of this dazzling duo, from a long-unsolved murder to
a terrifying kidnapping. And of course every adventure is stocked with all
the suspense, wit, glamour, and wonder you'd expect from the Queen.
 
